<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
     <p xml:id="Aink208-kilavi"> cevilik kaṟattoṭu niṉṟa tōḻi yavaḷāl varaivu māṭcimaippaṭṭapiṉpiva ḷivvāṟupaṭṭa varuttamellā niṉṉiṟ ṟīrnta teṉpatu kuṟippiṟ ṟoṉṟa vavaṭkuc colliyatu. </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante, who stood up with virtue to the foster-mother, told her, as it appeared through signs that “all the suffering she (i.e., the heroine) experienced in this way was alleviated because of you (i.e., the foster-mother),” after the marriage became honourable by her (i.e., the confidante).</p>
      </div>
       <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink208">
<l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai kāṉavar</l>
<l>kiḻaṅkakaḻ neṭuṅkuḻi malka vēṅkaip</l>
<l>poṉmali putuvīt tāa mavarnāṭṭu</l>
<l>maṇiniṟa mālvarai maṟaitoṟiva</l>
<l>ḷaṟaimalar neṭuṅka ṇārntaṉa paṉiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>
<l rend="space"> Whenever the sapphire-hued, dark mountain with his land, </l>
<l rend="indent">where gold, abundant newly mature blossoms of the East Indian Kino tree spread, </l>
<l rend="indent">such that the deep pit, from which forest people excavate bulbous roots, is filled, </l>
<l>was concealed [from her view], </l>
<l rend="space">her long, flower-petal eyes filled with dew.</l>

 </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
